      value: 1.2
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5122842465899161861, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "Draxt \u012B \u0100s\u016Br\u012Bg ( \"The Babylonian Tree\")\n\nIn
        X'anirala land \nthere is no tree of my stature. \nBecause the kings eat
        of me \nwhen I bear first fruits. \nI am the plank for boats; \nI am the
        mast for sails. \nThey make brooms of me \nwhich sweep house and home \nThey
        make presses of me \nwhich pound barley and rice. \nI am shoes for farmers;
        \nI am cushions for the barefoot. \nThey make ropes of me \nwhich bind thy
        legs. \nThey make clubs of me \nwhich break thy neck. \nThey make pegs of
        me \nwhich hang thee head downwards. \nI am fuel for fires \nwhich they roast
        thy flesh. \nIn summer  am shade \nover the head of rulers \nI am vinegar
        for farmers, \nhoney for noblemen. \nam a nest for little birds \nshade for
        travellers. \nEven those persons \nwho have neither wine nor bread \neat
        fruit from me \nuntil they become full"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5122842465899161861, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_TextStyleHashCode
      value: -1183493901
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5431834928911583797, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 4ff87bb8ffb98e04fa394d6d4ff3e322, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 5488519469664222319, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: in southern Iran, Palms are to this day counted not in Units but in
        persons.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5902464882853280731, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: instanceId
      value: f6cadfa0-8c3d-49be-a029-bcb29ff3378c
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5956918439778082410, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Plutarch Table Talk:

        But the palm-tree, which sheds none of
        the leaves that grow on it, is truly always in leaf, and it is this strength
        that it has which people particularly associate with the vigour that brings
        victory.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5956918439778082416, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: Across the near east and mediterranean it spread, withstanding the harsh
        desert Climate and dry nature
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5956918439778082416, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_TextStyleHashCode
      value: -1183493901
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6181259333930047258, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: GsplatAsset
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 4599839170941234424, guid: f178e50e8942e2a4fa0cfa1a3ef240b6, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 6181259333930047258, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_assetGuid
      value: f178e50e8942e2a4fa0cfa1a3ef240b6
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6835627233580907840, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 398f53a9fdcc0fc418985782f3d04078, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 7173199714940506848, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: In the Poem, a date Palm and a goat argue About who is worth more to
        humans
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7173199714940506848, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
